<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪怀疑地看着小男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不怕我吗？”妖怪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不怕。”小男孩儿说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得怕你吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。”妖怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要吃了你。你不怕吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿耸耸肩。“没那么可怕。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪犹豫了一下，然后靠近了一点儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，那个小男孩儿变成了悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抽出了金箍棒打了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪向后跳了一下，躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空没打中他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”妖怪大声问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是孙悟空。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你太坏了！居然吃孩子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空？”妖怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以为你被困在五指山下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你在这里干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我出来了。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在正护送唐僧去西天取经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪的眼睛亮了。“唐僧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空打了过去。妖怪转身消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空回到了老陈家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把发生的一切告诉了大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多亏你的帮助，我的儿子才能活下来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老陈说，“谢谢你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不客气。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我觉得那妖怪现在想抓我师父了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天一早，我们必须找到船离开。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>与此同时，妖怪正坐在河底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我必须抓住唐僧吃了他。”他自言自语地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有那猴子在，唐僧就不容易抓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我得用点儿法术。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>深夜，一阵寒风刮过，雪花开始一片片飘落。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒睡不着。“这里太冷了。”他自言自语道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看悟空和悟净。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个人都睡得很香。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们睡得真香。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们的毯子一定比我的暖和。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，悟空醒来，冻得发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨晚真......真是太冷了。”他自言自语道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好冷啊！”他看了看自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“难怪我冷！我的毯子呢？”悟净也醒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么这么......阿嚏！冷？我的毯子呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看着八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒盖着三条毯子睡得正香。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从头到脚盖得非常严实。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空踢了他一下。“起来！小偷！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒翻了个身，在毯子里咯咯笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净皱了皱眉头。“你偷了我们的......阿嚏！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空挠了挠脑袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么这么冷？现在是春天啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打开窗户，大吃一惊。“昨晚下雪了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们叫醒了唐僧和老陈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家走到屋外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一层厚厚的积雪盖住了整个村子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这样的天气过河会很危险的。”老陈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们最好等雪融化再走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个村民跑了过来。“河里结冰了！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这消息太好了！”唐僧笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以走过河了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧一行人谢过老陈后出发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快他们就站在了结冰的河边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“走过去是否会安全呢。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我用我的钉耙试试。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒走上了冰面，举起了钉耙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐当！他用力砸冰面，但那冰面并没有裂开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很结实。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧一行人都踏上了冰面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走了几个小时，可还是看不到河对岸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一声巨响，冰面开始颤动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么回事？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。”悟空说，“但我们还是......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>340340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>347735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咔嚓！在他们脚下，冰面裂开了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>